snippet.title: Evil Democracy: 1932 (PC Game Trailer)
snippet.description:
Soon on Steam!
Elections in Germany in 1932 were supposed to be different. The Nazis should not have won. Lead a political party and do not let them come to power. Win the WWII before it even begins. https://store.steampowered.com/app/1219950
